  <brief_title>Effects of Oral Care in the Neuroscience ICU</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comprehensive Oral Care for the Intubated Neuroscience ICU Patient: A Comparison of the Safety and Efficacy Between 2 Protocols</official_title>
